{"sections":[{"estimatedTimeInMinutes":15,"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"Learn how to dynamically change themes at runtime.","type":"text"}]}],"chapter":"Advanced","kind":"hero","title":"Change themes at runtime"},{"tasks":[{"contentSection":[{"kind":"fullWidth","content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"Before enabling theme changes at runtime, you need a mechanism to trigger the change. This tutorial assumes the change is user-driven through a UI. However, themes can also be changed programmatically without a UI.","type":"text"}]}]}],"title":"Create a view to change the theme","anchor":"Create-a-view-to-change-the-theme","stepsSection":[{"caption":[],"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"Create a file named ","type":"text"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"ThemeChangerView.swift"},{"type":"text","text":"."}]}],"media":null,"code":"02-01-01-code-0001.swift","runtimePreview":null,"type":"step"},{"caption":[],"runtimePreview":null,"code":"02-01-01-code-0002.swift","content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"Access the ","type":"text"},{"code":"ThemeManager","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":" instance from the environment."}]}],"type":"step","media":null},{"caption":[{"inlineContent":[{"text":"This is required because ","type":"text"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"ThemeManager"},{"text":" is marked as an ","type":"text"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"@Observable"},{"type":"text","text":" type."}],"type":"paragraph"}],"code":"02-01-01-code-0003.swift","content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"In the view’s body, create a binding to the "},{"code":"ThemeManager","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":" instance.","type":"text"}]}],"type":"step","media":null,"runtimePreview":null},{"code":"02-01-01-code-0004.swift","type":"step","media":null,"runtimePreview":null,"caption":[],"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Next, add the basic structure of the 